cd CozyUI
npm install
npm run dev
# Open http://localhost:5173
```

## Project Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── nodes/              # React Flow custom nodes
│   ├── StatusBar.jsx       # Memory + status indicators
│   ├── Sidebar.jsx         # Node palette
